(43, '1', 1, 'Yuichi', 'Kimura', '', 'Born in 1948 in Tokyo.\r\nSince graduating from university in Fine Art, he has taught university-level Plastic (formative) Art, been an art lecturer at a community college and worked as a presenter on a children''s television programme.\r\nHe has published over 300 titles to date, in an increasingly diverse range of genres (e.g. writing and illustrating fairytales and picture books and writing dramas and comics) and his work is highly praised all over the world.', 'yuichi_kimura_big.jpg', '', '', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-11-20 11:24:03', 62, 1),
(44, '1,2', 1, 'Naomi', 'Kojima', '', 'Born in Tokyo in 1950. Author and illustrator of picture books. Spent part of her childhood in New York and her college years in Memphis, Tennessee, graduating from Rhodes College.\r\nAfter teaching art at an international school in Tokyo, she once again returned to the United States, where she published her first children''s books.\r\nShe now lives in Tokyo, writing and illustrating books for children in English and Japanese. ', 'naomi_kojima_big.jpg', '', '', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-13 18:19:53', 62, 1),
