(53, '1,3', 1, 'Manabu', 'Miyazaki', '', 'Born in 1949, Miyazaki worked in a company before becoming a self taught professional photographer in 1972. His work was a breath of fresh air in the world of wildlife photography, and he has won many awards for his picture books and photography. He is currently active as a ''photographer of news from the natural world''.', 'manabu_miyazaki_b.jpg', 'http://www.owlet.net/', 'Japanese only', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-13 18:23:18', 62, 1),
