(59, '1,3', 1, 'Hiromi', 'Nagakura', '', 'Born in 1952 in Hokkaido. Photographer. After graduating from university, Nagakura worked as a press agency photographer. Since 1980 he has visited and taken photos of the disputed areas in Africa, the Middle East, Mid South America and Southeast Asia. Simultaneously, he has continued to watch Afghanistan.\r\nHe has received many awards and journalist prizes in Japan.', 'hiromi_nagakura_b.jpg', '', '', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-13 18:25:30', 62, 1),
