(105, '1', 1, 'Nahoko', 'Uehashi', '', 'Born in 1962 in Tokyo, Uehashi completed a PhD in Cultural Anthropology (focusing on Australian Aborigines) and is now a professor.\r\nThe fantasy novels in Uehashi''s ''MORIBITO (Guardian) Series'', which draw heavily on her Cultural Anthropology studies, have won many awards in Japan.', 'nahoko_uehashi_b.jpg', '', '', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-18 11:15:13', 62, 1),
