(163, '1,2', 1, 'Iku', 'Dekune', '', 'Born in Tokyo in 1969. In 1992, she graduated from Musashino Art University, majoring in printmaking.\r\nHer etchings on Grimm''s Fairy Tales were selected in 1998 for the Bologna Children''s Book Fair Illustrations.\r\nIn 1999, her works on Grimm were exhibited in Kassel and at the Museums of the Brothers Grimm in Steinau, Germany.\r\nIn 2003, the picture-book "The Sea Hare (Parol-sha) " was awarded the Grand-Prix at the Biennial of Illustrations Bratislava.\r\nSince 2002 she has lived in Prague.', 'iku_dekune_big.jpg', '', '', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-02-26 14:19:48', 62, 1),
