(278, '1', 1, 'Katsumi', 'Komagata', '', 'Born 1953 in Shizuoka Prefecture, Komagata moved to America in 1977 and worked as a graphic designer in the Book Department of CBS in New York. In 1986, he returned to Japan and set up his own company, One Stroke. Most of his books can also be found in art galleries both throughout Japan and overseas. He currently holds workshops around the world, where his wide readership of people from all generations can communicate and share ideas.', 'katsumi_komagata.jpg', 'http://www.one-stroke.co.jp/', '', '2008-11-12 18:40:35', 62, '2012-02-23 01:38:22', 62, 1),
