(50, 6, 'Choo-choo', 15, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 3, '', '', 'Another simple, but highly effective picture book by this prolific illustrator, who has already published a number of titles abroad. The pictures show a little train on its journey through the countryside, over hill and dale, and finally into the city.', '', '', '', '', '1988-12-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'tgspb_choochoo_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(51, 6, 'Zzzzz...', 15, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 3, '|8|', '', 'The ''ZZZZZ...'' of the title extends through the pages of the book as a mosquito makes its way from one animal to the next. A frog, hippopotamus, kangaroo and other animals get stung. The little insect meets its match when it lands on a tortoise.', '', '', '', '', '1991-05-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'tgspb_zzzzz_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-02-23 20:32:58', 62, 1),
(52, 6, 'Rrrrr...', 15, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 3, '', '', 'A small propeller-driven airplane appears in the deep blue sky. It approaches, passes through a white cloud, then a black cloud. Suddenly the empty page is filled with other little planes, and the quiet little story ends on a dramatic note.', '', '', '', '', '1991-05-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'tgspb_rrrrr_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 16:53:13', 62, 1),
(53, 6, 'Ddddd...', 15, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 3, '', '', 'A bulldozer goes about its work in a chugging rhythm, up and down the music scales. In this series of simple onomatopoeic picture books, Gomi breaks new ground in both text and style of illustration.', '', '', '', '', '1992-10-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'tgspb_ddddd_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 16:44:41', 62, 1),
(54, 6, 'Te te te te te...', 15, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 3, '', '', 'In Japan ''te'' means ''hand'', as well as being equivalent to the English verb ending ''ing''. Coupling these two meanings, Gomi creates a simple and delightful picture book showing hands doing things.', '', '', '', '', '1993-02-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'tgspb_tetetetete_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 16:53:37', 62, 1),
(55, 6, 'Ha ha ha ha ha...', 15, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 3, '', '', 'Japanese words beginning with ''ha'' are the theme of this ''sound picture book''. They include a bee, dove, box, paintbrush, lotus root, bald man and bridge. Gomi depicts both animate and inanimate objects with the same sense of life and fun.', '', '', '', '', '1993-06-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'tgspb_hahahahaha_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 16:45:00', 62, 1),
(56, 6, 'Bi bi bi bi bi...', 15, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 3, '', '', 'Gomi uses the sound ''bibibibibi'' to create a tiny insect-like creature with the impact of an electric charge. In this book the impish ''bibibibibi'' goes on a mischievous romp from rabbit to cat to elephant before arriving at his final destination - a television set.', '', '', '', '', '1994-06-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'tgspb_bibibibi_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 16:44:25', 62, 1),
(57, 6, 'Nu nu nu nu nu...', 15, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 3, '', '', 'What does the sound ''nu'' suggest to you? To illustrator, it manifests itself in a whole range of objects, actions and feelings - from a globular monster to an old man in his rocking-chair, a woman relaxing in a bath and a child practising Japanese-style fencing.', '', '', '', '', '1994-06-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'tgspb_nununununu_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 16:52:42', 62, 1),
(58, 6, 'Ri ri ri ri ri...', 15, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 3, '', '', 'After a work the illustrator is relaxing in his room when he hears a faint sound. He decides to follow it through the quiet streets of the sleeping town, passing through cityscapes: across a river, among high-rise buildings, through a children''s playground.', '', '', '', '', '1995-01-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'tgspb_ririririri_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 16:52:57', 62, 1),
(59, 6, 'Nnnnn...', 15, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 3, '', '', 'A dog finds a round black object lying in the path. The object turns out to be a bird, which the dog begins to tease, unaware that the bird''s mother is watching from above. What a surprise for the dog when mother bird swoops down and picks him up in her claws!', '', '', '', '', '1995-04-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'tgspb_nnnnn_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 16:45:53', 62, 1),
(60, 0, 'Sign of the Clouds', 54, 1, 0, 0, '', 129, 0, 0, 0, 1, 14, '', '', 'Kuroi depicts scenes of north-eastern Japan, where poet Kenji Miyazawa lived and worked. Many of Miyazawa''s poems are inspired by his feel for the changing seasons and in particular the clouds, the sky and the quality of light.', '', '', '', '', '1995-09-01 00:00:00', '36 x 27', '48', 1, 'kk_signofclouds_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(61, 0, 'Television Games', 15, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|10|', '', 'A boy who plays in the fields meets a strange man watching television. What a surprise when a lion jumps out of the screen! But then the man switches channels, and the boy finds himself in the sea. Another switch of channels brings a herd of stampeding elephants.', '', '', '', '', '1996-09-01 00:00:00', '27 x 21', '32', 1, 'tg_televisiongames_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(62, 0, 'Gadorufu''s Lily', 54, 1, 0, 0, '', 225, 0, 0, 0, 1, 14, '', '', 'A traveller caught in a thunderstorm takes refuge in a wayside house. As the storm rages, the traveller''s attention is drawn to a lily blooming outside. ''My love is like that flower. Don''t break!'' he thinks. The image of the delicate lily standing up to the violent wind and rain, like a person enduring a difficult fate, is a truly inspiring tale.', 'Award', '1995 SHOGAKUKAN AWARD FOR ILLUSTRATIONS FOR CHILDREN', '', '', '1996-11-01 00:00:00', '31 x 22', '32', 1, 'km_gadorufuslily_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 17:05:42', 62, 1),
(63, 0, 'Lost and Found', 15, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, '|10|', '', 'A boy digging a hole discovers a hat which he lost in the summer before, a ball which he lost in the spring and a pair of gloves which he lost in the winter. As he continues to dig he uncovers more objects from his past. The last object which he digs up is the cradle that he used as a baby.', '', '', '', '', '1997-01-01 00:00:00', '27 x 21', '32', 1, 'tg_lostandfound_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(64, 0, 'The Helicopters', 15, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, '|10|', '', 'Two helicopters meet up in the forest and set off together on a journey through a storm at sea. After resting, they come to a small town. On the top of a church, one of the helicopters gives birth to a multitude of baby helicopters which fly off into the sky like so many little butterflies.', '', '', '', '', '1997-04-01 00:00:00', '27 x 21', '32', 1, 'tg_helicopters_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(65, 0, 'Son''s Way', 15, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, '|10|', '', 'Companion book to ''Mother''s Way'' depicts what happens in the real world. Mother''s favourite son slurps up his noodles straight from the bowl, plays percussion on the kitchen pans, keeps worms as pets, crashes his toy cars... ', '', '', '', '', '1998-09-01 00:00:00', '27 x 21', '32', 1, 'tg_sonsway_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(66, 0, 'Mother''s Way', 15, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, '|10|', '', 'This picture book shows how an average mother would like to be in a perfect world. She would like her son to eat nutritious meals, have clean habits, practise his music everyday, keep goldfish, learn the tea ceremonyÉ', '', '', '', '', '1998-09-01 00:00:00', '27 x 21', '32', 1, 'tg_mothersway_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
