(650, 0, 'Animal Picture Book', 12, 1, 0, 0, '', 201, 0, 0, 0, 1, 2, '', '', 'Another delightful pop-up and activity book from the team that brought us the popular Things to Ride In 1 & 2. An adventurous little chick sets off around the zoo to greet all of her animal friends. Featuring colourful pull-outs and bold illustrations, it is both educational and enjoyable. Includes English spelling and pronunciation for little learners, too. ', '', '', '', '', '2009-09-09 00:00:00', '16 x 22', '26', 1, '127060animal_picture_book.jpg', '2009-11-29 12:26:37', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
