(305, 21, 'Kotaro the Bandit', 64, 1, 0, 0, '', 192, 0, 0, 0, 2, 10, '', '', 'Revised version of a best-selling story set in late medieval Japan. Kotaro, a boy with amazing strength, swears to take revenge on a villainous warlord who was responsible for the deaths of his parents. Together with a young swordsman and ninja he forms a group of bandits based in the mountains. The novel follows their adventures.', '', '', '', '', '2002-11-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '206', 2, 'kb_kotarothebandit_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(306, 21, 'The Boy in the Hot Air Balloon', 64, 1, 0, 0, '', 192, 0, 0, 0, 2, 10, '', '', 'Kotaro the bandit is joined by Jiromaru, a boy who returned to Japan in a hot air balloon after studying science in Italy under a student of Leonardo da Vinci. Jiromaru helps Kotaro and his friends to make various weapons for use in their fight against the evil samurai general Judaiyu and the magician Oboro. Sequel to "Kotaro the Bandit."', '', '', '', '', '2003-01-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '214', 2, 'kb_boyinthehotairballoon_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(307, 21, 'Yakumo''s Battle', 64, 1, 0, 0, '', 192, 0, 0, 0, 2, 10, '', '', 'Kotaro has joined forces with his bandit friends and pirates to hunt down some of their enemies. The liveliness of the children makes for a great story. The concluding part of ''Kotaro the Bandit''.', '', '', '', '', '2004-01-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '214', 2, 'kb_yakumosbattle_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
