(350, 0, 'Taruto and the Cake Seeds', 69, 1, 0, 0, '', 190, 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, '', '', 'Taruto and his younger sister Colita''s adventure begins when they find a picture of a cake seed in a book on their bookshelf at home. They set off towards the forest on the hill in search of some, so that they can bake them and enjoy some cakes for themselves!', '', '', '', '', '2006-06-01 00:00:00', '19 x 24', '32', 1, 'tarutoandthecakeseeds_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(351, 0, 'The Red Candle and the Mermaid', 70, 1, 0, 0, '', 80, 0, 0, 0, 1, 14, '|2|11|', '', 'A mermaid leaves her baby on the shore of a seaside village to be raised by an old couple. The girl grows and works decorating candles which are sold as lucky charms to placate the sea god. However, when the couple betray the girl by selling her to a greedy merchant, the same candles become a symbol of the vengeful feelings of the girl''s mother.', '', '', '', '', '2002-01-01 00:00:00', '22 x 20', '32', 1, 'ks_redcandlemermaid_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 12:53:20', 62, 1),
(352, 27, 'Yokoshima-kun (Stripy The Ferret)', 71, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 14, '|24|2|11|', '', 'Stripy is a white ferret that always wears a bluestriped T-shirt. He is a show - off and a liar, as well as being lazy, rude and bad - tempered. But today Stripy''s horoscope says that it''s an excellent opportunity for making a friend. Will he succeed in doing so?', '', '', '', '', '2002-11-01 00:00:00', '19 x 14', '64', 1, 'yokoshimakstf_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 16:56:15', 62, 1),
(353, 27, 'Yokoshima-kun and Pink-chan', 71, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 14, '|24|2|11|', '', 'Over-confident Yokoshima-kun is a ferret who always wears a blue - striped shirt and Pink-chan is the quiet but equally determined girl next door. Aimed at older children, this picture book delights with its sharp character insights that poke fun at our human foibles.', '', '', '', '', '2003-11-01 00:00:00', '19 x 14', '64', 1, 'yokoshimakapc_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 16:57:03', 62, 1),
(354, 27, 'The Yokoshima-kun Theatre', 71, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 14, '|11|', '', 'This is a collection of every-day short stories of Yokoshima-kun and his friends. The book is made up of short episodes which are both funny and somewhat unusual. You might already know someone like Yokoshima-kun. ', '', '', '', '', '2005-11-01 00:00:00', '19 x 14', '64', 1, 'theyokoshimaks_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(355, 0, 'My Elder Sister', 72, 1, 0, 0, '', 181, 0, 0, 0, 2, 11, '|11|', '', 'Six stories all built around physically-handicapped children. They have a strong storyline and do not patrpnise the target audience.', 'Award', '1988 AKAITORI AWARD FOR ILLUSTRATIONS\r\n1987 JAPANESE ASSOCIATION OF WRITERS FOR CHILDREN NEW COMER PRIZE\r\n1989 NIIMI NANKICHI AWARD\r\n1988 TSUBOTA JOJI AWARD', '', '', '1986-12-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '182', 2, 'myeldersister_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 17:08:32', 62, 1),
(356, 0, 'The Extra-Curricular Timetable', 73, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '|10|11|14|', '', 'I am an elementary school craft teacher, and one day I saved a mouse from being eaten by a cat, but this mouse was no ordinary mouse: it could speak our language. From then on, every Monday after class it came to tell me strange stories about occurrences in the school. A well-constructed, humorous fantasy.', 'Award', '1981 JAPANESE ASSOCIATION OF WRITERS FOR CHILDREN NEW COMER PRIZE', '', '', '1980-07-01 00:00:00', '19 x 13', '197', 2, 'theextract_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 16:48:23', 62, 1),
(357, 0, 'Welcome to Bonus Time!', 73, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 11, '|10|', '', 'When the school bell goes, Ken''s classroom becomes full of thorns and he is unable to move. After he falls in and out of this world several times, he hits upon a successful idea and releases all the children in the school. Eventually, these parallel world occurrences make hitherto unfriendly classmates come together as friends.', '', '', '', '', '1981-07-01 00:00:00', '19 x 13', '220', 2, 'welcometobt_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(358, 0, 'Sheltering from the Rain under a Slide', 73, 1, 0, 0, '', 128, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '|10|11|', '', 'One summer day, twelve children living in the same block of flats are sheltering from the rain under a slide in a park when they begin to talk about Mr. Amamori, a man from their block. All of the children have had mysterious experiences with Mr. Amamori. Is he dabbling in magic?', '', '', '', '', '1983-10-01 00:00:00', '19 x 13', '165', 2, 'shelteringfromtruas_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 13:25:32', 62, 1),
(359, 0, 'The Starry Tale Request', 73, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '|10|11|', '', 'When a strange bird landed on my balcony, I began to tell him about the stars: a real story about a fake star, a maybe true story about a maybe real star, and an unbelievable story about a real star. Then I asked him for a real story about a real starÉ', '', '', '', '', '1983-12-01 00:00:00', '19 x 13', '156', 2, 'thestarrytr_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 17:03:03', 62, 1),
(360, 0, 'A Two Minute Adventure', 73, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 11, '|8|10|11|', '', '"Will you take out this thorn for me?" Led by a cat who suddenly starts to speak to him, Satoru sets off to kill a dragon. Satoru faces many difficulties in a world populated by children, and finally understands what is absolutely certain. This is the story of a breathless adventure that lasts for only two minutes. ', '', '', '', '', '1985-04-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '237', 2, 'atwominnutea_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-02-24 15:51:35', 62, 1),
(361, 0, 'Catching the School Rabbit', 73, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '|10|', '', 'Masako, a transfer student, has accidentally let one of the school rabbits escape, and it is hiding under a workman''s hut. How will the children try to recapture it on their own? A simple story of friendship taking place on a construction site in the evening.', '', '', '', '', '1986-11-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '160', 2, 'catchingtsr_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(362, 0, 'Billy Bottom the Little God', 73, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '|10|11|14|', '', 'Billy Bottom is the name of a little man with wings, who appears before the children in Hajime''s class. The strange thing is that the boy or girl he appears before always gets the lowest marks that day. A story which says that there is more to life than being top of the class.', 'Award', '1993 ROBO-NO-ISHI AWARD', '', '', '1988-10-01 00:00:00', '23 x 16', '164', 2, 'bbthelittledog_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(363, 0, 'Poanan''s Smell', 73, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'The big frog Poanan swallows soap and, thinking himself a bearer of justice, imprisons everyone that he believes to be doing bad things inside of soap bubbles. Unexpectedly, Hiroshi goes to save Yoko after she is captured inside a bubble and begins to fight with PoananÉ In the end, they find a surprising way to beat Poanan. ', '', '', '', '', '1989-10-01 00:00:00', '19 x 13', '164', 2, 'poananss_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(364, 0, 'A Hand-printed Tale', 73, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'Two children visiting their recently widowed uncle become involved in an adventure after he shows them a pair of crocodile''s eyes, which he has painted on his right hand, and some apples painted on his left one. The adventure helps the children to solve the riddle of the last word spoken by their dying aunt.', '', '', '', '', '1992-03-01 00:00:00', '23 x 16', '132', 2, 'ahandprintedt_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(365, 0, 'Involuntary Adventure', 73, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 11, '|10|', '', 'A computer game entitled ''Legend of the Shining Stone'' leads Manabu and Akari into a parallel world ruled by a king of darkness and his animal minions. As the fascinating story unfolds and the children traverse the parallel worlds, the line between fantasy and reality becomes increasingly blurred.', '', '', '', '', '1997-03-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '318', 2, 'involuntraya_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-02-23 20:34:31', 62, 1),
(366, 0, 'The Mysterious Timetable', 73, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '|10|', '', 'A collection of short stories dealing with many mysterious occurrences taking place in a schoolÉMidori, a shy first grader, cannot go anywhere other than the toilet by herself. When she has to go to the nurse''s room, a black cat appears, leading her by stepping on the tiles the same colour as his body. Midori follows suitÉ ', '', '', '', '', '1998-07-01 00:00:00', '22 x 15', '164', 2, 'themysterioust_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(367, 0, 'How to Become a Dragon-slaying Knight', 73, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 11, '|10|', '', 'Two children secretly enter their school one evening and there discover a man dressed as a medieval European knight. He says that he is waiting for a dragon to slay. As the evening goes on, some strange things happenÉ', '', '', '', '', '2003-11-01 00:00:00', '20 x 14', '110', 2, 'howtobecomeadsk_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(368, 0, 'Monaural', 74, 1, 0, 0, '', 129, 0, 0, 0, 1, 14, '', '', 'People waiting for a bus, green mountains on the skyline... Everyday scenes like these occasionally stick in our minds. This collection records such moments in quiet soft colours, leading the reader back into the world of memory and forward into the world of the imagination.', '', '', '', '', '1990-07-01 00:00:00', '33 x 25', '64', 1, 'kk_monaural_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(369, 0, 'The Sky is Yellow', 76, 1, 0, 0, '', 173, 0, 0, 0, 2, 13, '', '', 'Alisa and Nishida are very similar. So even when they are apart, they know what the other one is thinking. A story about the relationship and friendship between these two elementary school students.', '', '', '', '', '2004-08-01 00:00:00', '20 x 14', '126', 1, 'theskyisyellow_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(370, 0, 'The Golden Fish', 77, 1, 50, 4, '', 245, 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, '', '', 'An old fisherman catches a magic fish that offers to grant him any wish in return for its freedom. The fisherman lets the fish go, but is later scolded by his wife, who makes him confront the fish with a series of outrageous demands.', '', '', '', '', '2003-11-01 00:00:00', '29 x 25', '32-36', 1, 'goldenfish_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(371, 0, 'Sieg', 79, 1, 0, 0, '', 221, 0, 0, 0, 2, 13, '', '', 'Born from the blood of rival kingdoms but brought up in the forest by a wolf hunter, Sieg sets out on a mission to fulfil his destiny by destroying the evil god Argis.', '', '', '', '', '1992-04-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '294 & 238', 2, 'hs_sieg_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(372, 0, 'My Uncle', 79, 1, 0, 0, '', 177, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'The only thing that Nao, an eleven-year-old boy, knows about his uncle is that he disappeared ten years ago and has not been seen since. Then, one day a man wearing a white Indian robe appears. During that summer, the uncle, who has become a yogi, shows Nao some of the wonderful things he can do. ', '', '', '', '', '1993-04-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '174', 2, 'hs_myuncle_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(373, 0, 'Come Alone', 79, 1, 0, 0, '', 217, 0, 0, 0, 2, 11, '', '', 'A collection of seven original ghost stories in modern settings featuring young protagonists. Titles include The Old Purple Woman, Good Evening from the Ceiling, The Fox''s Mask, A Place in the Other World, The Fujimi Tunnel and Shinji''s Fishing Road.', '', '', '', '', '1994-06-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '174', 2, 'hs_comealone_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(374, 26, 'The Genpei War', 79, 1, 0, 0, '', 235, 0, 0, 0, 2, 13, '', '', 'The fox''s ability to adopt various disguises, even human ones, is a common ingredient of Japanese folk stories, and often incorporated into Kabuki and other traditional dramatic arts. In this novel, the author adopts one such fox as his central character in a story about warring samurai clans of the 12th century.', '', '', '', '', '1996-02-01 00:00:00', '19 x 14', '222-362', 2, 'hsdw_genpeiwar_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(375, 26, 'The Mongol Invasion', 79, 1, 0, 0, '', 235, 0, 0, 0, 2, 13, '', '', '80 years after the Genpei War, the fox wakes up in the Kamakura Period after a long, long sleep. Tokimune Hojo is in power and the former army is closing in. ', '', '', '', '', '1998-06-01 00:00:00', '19 x 14', '222-362', 2, 'hsdw_mongolinvasion_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(376, 0, 'The Tiger without Stripes', 79, 1, 0, 0, '', 170, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'Five stories about a bison without horns, a mongoose with a short tail, a snake with feet, an octopus with ten legs and a tiger without stripes. The tales relate how the animals use a mixture of ingenuity and courage to turn their differences into something positive.', '', '', '', '', '1999-06-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '142', 2, 'hs_tigerwostripes_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(377, 26, 'Fire in the Imperial Capital', 79, 1, 0, 0, '', 235, 0, 0, 0, 2, 13, '', '', 'A fox whose training with a mountain mystic has given it magical powers and eternal life witnesses key events in a turbulent period of medieval Japan. As samurai clans participate in a bloody power struggle involving the emperor and his family, the fox searches for an answer to the question: Why can''t humans live in peace?', '', '', '', '', '2000-05-01 00:00:00', '19 x 14', '222-362', 2, 'hsdw_fireinimperialcapital_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(378, 0, 'Sieg 2', 79, 1, 0, 0, '', 221, 0, 0, 0, 2, 13, '', '', 'Sieg leaves his native Silvania to cross the sea to Goldonia, the land of his father, where a mysterious destructive power is laying waste the land. The culprit turns out to be an ambitious and evil princess.', '', '', '', '', '2001-03-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '294 & 238', 2, 'hs_sieg2_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(379, 0, 'The Elephant''s Gold Medals', 79, 1, 0, 0, '', 234, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'How willl the elephant get on in the Olympics?! He''s taking part in weight-lifting, the discus, baseball, football, swimming and the marathon. I wonder how many gold medals he''ll win.', '', '', '', '', '2004-07-01 00:00:00', '26 x 22', '32', 1, 'hs_elephantgoldmedals_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(380, 0, 'Welcome from the Back', 79, 1, 0, 0, '', 217, 0, 0, 0, 2, 11, '', '', 'Welcome to the Ghost Story Club. The 7 participants who are taking it in turns to tell each other ghost stories about dolls are inviting you to join their slightly strange world. The sequel to ''Come Alone''. ', '', '', '', '', '2004-10-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '202', 2, 'hs_welcomefromback_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(381, 26, 'The Clouds of Civil War', 79, 1, 0, 0, '', 235, 0, 0, 0, 2, 13, '', '', 'The instruments of war begin to change from bows to guns. The fox meets a boy who has a gun and seeks a chance to avenge himself on Nobunaga Oda for his master''s death. The novel tells of Nobunaga''s victorious battles using guns, ending with his death at the hands of his two-faced vassal.', '', '', '', '', '2006-07-01 00:00:00', '19 x 14', '222-362', 2, 'hsdw_cloudsofcivilwar_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(382, 52, 'Igel''s Logbook Volume 1 The Fish-Man Priest', 79, 1, 0, 0, '', 257, 0, 0, 0, 2, 11, '', '', 'Karl impulsively boards a secret submarine that is off to investigate a mysterious wanted doctor''s hypothesis about a huge vortex. In a cave, Karl and the crew discover hundreds of fish-men wearing armour! Then they realise that they are expected to beat up the monster birds. Can they save the kingdom of the fish-men?', '', '', '', '', '2007-11-01 00:00:00', '20 x 14', '230', 2, '112007igelslogbook_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-02-14 09:44:49', 62, 1),
(383, 0, 'Rico''s House', 80, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|0|11|', '', 'The first picture book by a designer of traditional textiles tells the tale of a little girl who creates her own make-believe home in a box so that she can escape from her bossy elder brother. A story which will inspire younger readers to create their own playworlds.', '', '', '', '', '1998-10-01 00:00:00', '25 x 19', '32', 1, 'ks_ricoshouse_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-04 16:44:31', 62, 1),
(384, 0, 'Night Bear', 80, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|8|10|11|', '', 'One night a little boy is visited by a baby bear searching for its mother. Together the two go into the town to try to find her, but she is not there. Neither is she at home. Where can she be? Finally, a shooting star takes them to her. At the end of the tale, the little boy is asleep with his own teddy.', '', '', '', '', '1999-11-01 00:00:00', '19 x 25', '32', 1, 'ks_nightbear_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 17:02:19', 62, 1),
(385, 0, ' Friday''s Sugar', 80, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 14, '', '', 'Time seems to stand still in these three episodes: a baby girl who has gone to sleep in the grass is guarded by a mantis until her mother comes, a boy makes a discovery on his way home from school and a little girl explores the house while her parents sleep. Delicate artistic pictures convey a sense of wonder.', 'Award', '2005 THE BIENNIAL OF ILLUSTRATIONS BRATISLAVA PLAQUE', '', '', '2003-10-01 00:00:00', '19 x 14', '61', 1, 'ks_fridayssugar_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(386, 0, 'The Horse Egg', 81, 1, 0, 0, '', 220, 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, '', '', 'This folk tale from Bengal tells of a gullible man who buys a pumpkin in the belief that it''s a horse egg. Worse still, he then mistakes a runaway fox for his newly hatched horse! A dynamic and amusing story develops, with the man chasing the fox, then a monkey and finally a tiger.', '', '', '', '', '2003-06-01 00:00:00', '29 x 25', '32-36', 1, 'horseegg_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(387, 0, 'The Rainbow Lake', 82, 1, 0, 0, '', 178, 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, '', '', 'The lovely nymph of a lake is wooed unsuccessfully by a young magician. Brokenhearted, he tears a rainbow to pieces, after which the lake begins to shine in seven different colours. An elegantly illustrated legend from the north of Italy.', '', '', '', '', '1970-05-01 00:00:00', '27 x 21', '34-36', 1, 'ci_rainbowlake_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(388, 36, 'Leaf-cut Weevils', 83, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 143, 0, 4, 9, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '1996-11-01 00:00:00', '28 x 23', '40', 5, 'leafcutweevils_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(389, 0, 'Sorry, We Are Circles and Dot', 84, 1, 0, 0, '', 162, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'Circles are self-satisfied, rolling over as they please without the help of the wind. Dots want to be the centre of attention, unable to stay still and romping around. Also meet the quick-tempered triangle, the docile square, the enthusiastic straight line and the lazy limp line.', '', '', '', '', '2006-09-01 00:00:00', '22 x 21', '48', 1, 'sc_sorrywercirclesanddot_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(390, 0, 'I Wish I Had a Big, Big Tree', 85, 1, 0, 0, '', 202, 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, '|8|3|10|11|', '', 'Kaoru wanted his own giant tree. If he had one, he would climb it and watch the little birds and squirrels. At the very top would be a platform from which he could look far away.', 'Award', '1972 INTERNATIONAL BOOK DESIGN EXHIBITION AT LEIPZIG (Bronze Medal)', '', '', '1971-01-01 00:00:00', '26 x 21', '36', 1, 'iwishihadbigbigtree_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 13:40:00', 62, 1),
(391, 0, 'Granny''s Flying Machine', 85, 1, 0, 0, '', 202, 0, 0, 0, 1, 9, '', '', 'Entranced by the beautiful wings of a butterfly which lands on her lap, an old woman tries to reproduce the pattern in her knitting. When, after much time and effort, she succeeds, she discovers that the cloth has a life of its own and, like the wings, will carry her up into the air.', '', '', '', '', '1999-05-01 00:00:00', '29 x 25', '48', 1, 'grannysflyingmachine_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(392, 0, 'Summer Time - Pianists and the Four Seasons Part1 -', 86, 1, 0, 0, '', 196, 0, 0, 0, 2, 13, '|10|', '', 'Two stories for ''young adults'' are offered. The first introduces Hirokazu, a boy with one arm, whose mother is a jazz pianist, while the second describes the world of Kana, an adolescent girl living in a Tokyo newtown as she struggles to develop a positive self-image.', '', '', '', '', '1990-06-01 00:00:00', '19 x 14', '110', 2, 'summertimepatfs1_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(393, 0, 'Slow Motion', 86, 1, 0, 0, '', 196, 0, 0, 0, 2, 13, '|10|', '', 'In this novel, Sato focuses on the relationship between two young people with deep psychological wounds. ''Nii-chan'' is a young unemployed man with a rebellious past, while Shuko is a fragile, ''slow motion'' high-school student, whose father was a murderer.', '', '', '', '', '1993-04-01 00:00:00', '19 x 13', '190', 2, 'slowmotion_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(394, 0, 'September Rain - Pianists and the Four Seasons Part2 -', 86, 1, 0, 0, '', 196, 0, 0, 0, 2, 13, '|10|', '', 'In her sequel to ''Summer Time'', Sato develops and draws together the characters of Hirokazu, now sixteen, and Kana, who is approaching winter as a fourteen-year-old. In the title story, Hirokazu recalls impressions of his meeting with Kana.', '', '', '', '', '1993-05-01 00:00:00', '19 x 14', '110', 2, 'summertimepatfs2_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(395, 0, 'Life with an Iguana', 86, 1, 0, 0, '', 167, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '|10|', '', 'Iguanas are herbivorous, non-aggressive, clean reptiles which are not noisy and are friendly to human beings. In other words, they make the perfect pets.Or do they? Well, if you want to know, read this story about a girl who is given an iguana as a birthday present.', '', '', '', '', '1997-09-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '264', 2, 'lifewithaniguana_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(396, 0, 'The Adventure of the Dos Aguilas', 87, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 14, '|0|', '', 'Six explorers board a ship to go in search of a giant flying egg. During their travels they encounter a bird with a drill-shaped beak, are attacked by a group of whirlwinds, drink from a lime juice river and experience many other amazing adventures.', '', '', '', '', '2002-10-01 00:00:00', '26 x 22', '40', 1, 'st_adventureofdosaguilas_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 23:36:55', 62, 1),
(397, 0, 'The Glass Horse', 89, 1, 0, 0, '', 169, 0, 0, 0, 2, 7, '|10|', '', 'A boy breaks the leg of glass ornamental horse, only to see it run away. This starts a great adventure, at glass mountain, where he makes friends.', 'Award', '2002 NIIMI NANKICHI AWARD\r\n2002 NOMA AWARD FOR JUVENILE LITERATURE', '', '', '2001-10-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '158', 2, 'theglasshorse_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 17:09:33', 62, 1),
(398, 0, 'The Girl Who Became a Monster', 90, 1, 0, 0, '', 213, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'After watching her favourite monster programme, Michiko makes a wish - ''Turn me into a monster!'' What a surprise when she opens her eyes to find her wish granted. She is a monster, and her little sister, Mimi, a frog.', '', '', '', '', '1975-01-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '148', 2, 'girlwhobecameamonster_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(399, 0, 'Mummy, Guess!', 90, 1, 0, 0, '', 169, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|13|', '', 'One evening when a little girl wants to go out to play she makes up a game of riddles for her mother. What is it that''s round, red, big and beautiful? Finally Mummy guesses---the setting sun.', '', '', '', '', '1976-12-01 00:00:00', '24 x 20', '32', 1, 'mummyguess_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(400, 0, 'The Little Girl Who Returned to the Star', 90, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 13, '|10|', '', 'Mamiko''s working mother often returns home late. On her twelfth birthday Mamiko receives one of her mother''s old coats as a present. In a pocket she finds a bus ticket. Thus begins an adventure in which she travels back in time to meet her mother as a young woman and learn about a tragic incident that shaped her life.', 'Award', '1978 JAPANESE ASSOCIATION OF WRITERS FOR CHILDREN NEW COMER PRIZE\r\n1976 JAPAN JUVENILE WRITERS ASSOCIATION NEWCOMER PRIZE', '', '', '1977-03-01 00:00:00', '20 x 14', '270', 2, 'thelittlegirlwrtts_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 17:10:04', 62, 1),
(401, 0, 'Mr. Hide''n''Seek', 90, 1, 0, 0, '', 169, 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, '|10|11|', '', 'A little girl named Keiko wanders into a strange forest on her way home from the park and meets a boy who calls himself Mr. Hide ''n'' Seek of the Woods. A delightful story of a beautiful autumn forest and playing hide-and-seek with the animals who live there.', '', '', '', '', '1978-11-01 00:00:00', '26 x 21', '40', 1, 'mrhidenseek_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(402, 0, 'The Seven Magic Spells of Black Rose', 90, 1, 0, 0, '', 195, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'Stories about an old witch who looks just like middle-aged city woman. Despite her ability to fly and to turn herself into all sorts of animals and objects, Black Rose is subject to romantic weaknesses, pride and a desire to help the world, its people and herself.', '', '', '', '', '1991-10-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '148', 2, '7magicspellsofblackrose_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(403, 0, 'When the Rainflowers Bloomed', 90, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 13, '|10|16|', '', 'Alisa and Nishida are very similar. So even when they are apart, they know what the other one is thinking. A story about the relationship and friendship between these two elementary school students.', 'Award', '1999 SHOGAKUKAN CULTURAL PRIZE IN PUBLISHING FOR CHILDREN''S BOOKS', '', '', '1998-04-01 00:00:00', '20 x 14', '126', 1, 'whentherb_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 16:35:32', 62, 1),
(404, 0, 'The Magical Trip of Ms Black Rose', 90, 1, 0, 0, '', 195, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '|10|', '', 'Ms Black Rose, an old Japanese witch, is a bit down in the dumps these days. One day she goes on a trip in order to look for a missing young man, who studies at the Wizardry School in Germany. She finds that the school is not actually there, but instead she wanders into a fairyland.', '', '', '', '', '2007-02-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '302', 2, '072007magicaltripofmsbr_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 14:09:24', 62, 1),
(405, 0, 'Moonlight Bus', 91, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 7, '', '', 'Sporadic traffic travels along a coastal road. In the night sky the full moon shines. In the distant headland a lighthouse gleams. As a little boy waits to cross the road, a bus passes. When he looks into the bus he sees a magical world. Haunting story and illustrations.', '', '', '', '', '2002-10-01 00:00:00', '27 x 21', '24', 1, 'kk_moonlightbus_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(406, 0, 'My Bird Nest Picture Diary', 92, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 10, '|8|10|11|', '', 'Through the changing seasons, the narrator documents the local array of bird life, offering a beautifully illustrated picture diary about their daily lives, (nesting, feeding etc). An opportunity for parents to familiarize children with various birds and seasonal changes in a rural setting.', 'Award', '2006 THE KODANSHA CULTURAL PRIZE FOR CHILDREN''S PICTUREBOOK PUBLICATION', '', '', '2005-04-01 00:00:00', '29 x 25', '36', 1, 'mybirdnestpicturediary_big.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2010-09-05 04:58:35', 62, 1),
(407, 0, 'All About Bird Nests', 92, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, '|8|10|11|', '', 'In this follow up to his award winning book, My Bird Nest Picture Diary, Suzuki introduces a number of very different bird nests, all vividly depicted in his beautifully hand-drawn illustrations. He discusses why birds build nests where they do, how they build them and which materials they use - such as feathers and snakeskin.', '', '', '', '', '2006-04-01 00:00:00', '25 x 27', '32', 1, 'allaboutbirdnests_big.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2010-09-05 04:58:52', 62, 1),
(408, 0, 'Bird Nest Stories', 92, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, '|8|', '', 'The nest is the place where a bird''s life begins, and for every nest, there is a special story. All sorts of things take place in and around the wealth of different nests found in trees all around the world. Here, some of these exciting bird tales are set next to detailed, atmospheric illustrations. ', '', '', '', '', '2007-10-01 00:00:00', '28 x 26', '32', 1, '112007ms_birdneststories_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2010-09-05 04:59:15', 62, 1),
(409, 0, 'Unusual Birds Nests', 92, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 8, '|8|', '', 'A bird''s most important possession is its nest, which it must build very carefully in order to protect its eggs and chicks. This book explores some of the most unusual and fascinating nests built by birds around the world, explaining their structure, materials and construction in a lively and interesting way.', '', '', '', '', '2007-10-01 00:00:00', '27 x 23', '40', 1, '112007ms_unusualbirdsnests_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2010-09-05 04:59:27', 62, 1),
(410, 0, 'Kodomomo-chan(Child Peach)', 93, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'Kodomomo-chan the young peach, seems to be out of sorts today. All of her animal playmates wonder what is the matter with her. Finally, a kind mother bear helps out Kodomomo-chan and she can join in playing with her friends. ', '', '', '', '', '2005-06-01 00:00:00', '21 x 21', '32', 1, 'kodomomo-chan_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(411, 0, 'Let''s Go to Fun Forest', 94, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 6, '', '', 'This prize-winning illustrated book details the adventures of four children who, upon venturing into the local forest, meet Marubo, a creature shaped like a kettle who spouts hot water, and Bosako, who is covered in spiky hairs and has a tree growing from the top of his head. ', '', '', '', '', '1995-03-01 00:00:00', '21 x 16', '78', 3, 'ht_lets52funforest_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(412, 0, 'The Little Thieves of Fun Forest', 94, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 6, '', '', 'In the second title in the Fun Forest series, Marubo invites the children to a tea party in the forest, but has to come to their rescue on the way when they are abducted by a kidnapping tapir, a basketball orange and two robber rice cakes on a bike. ', '', '', '', '', '1997-03-01 00:00:00', '21 x 16', '80', 3, 'ht_littlethievesofff_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(413, 0, 'The Name Collector of Fun Forest', 94, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 6, '', '', 'On a trip to the Fun Forest, Marubo tells the children about the Namaemon - a creature who devours anyone or anything with a name, whereupon the name is recorded in a book on the creature''s head. The friends later find the Namaemon napping, and discover that he has eaten their friends Bosako and Ururinzo!', '', '', '', '', '1999-06-01 00:00:00', '21 x 16', '79', 3, 'ht_namecollectorofff_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(414, 0, 'Fancy-Free in Fun Forest', 94, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 6, '', '', 'Honrienu is a creature of the Fun Forest who loves reading, and is never seen without a book in her hand. The children find her distressed, however, because the main character of her current book, called Fancy-Free, has run off. The children help Honrienu track Fancy-Free down. ', '', '', '', '', '2003-11-01 00:00:00', '21 x 16', '88', 3, 'ht_fancyfreeinff_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(415, 0, 'Run and Pun, the Two Snowmen', 94, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 6, '', '', 'Every day, Run and Pun wear different hats and the jobs they do depend on the colours they choose. One day, neither of them wants to wear the blue hat and problems occur. ', '', '', '', '', '2004-11-01 00:00:00', '21 x 16', '64', 2, 'ht_runnpun2snowmen_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(416, 0, 'The Postman and the Drop Dragon', 94, 1, 0, 0, '', 224, 0, 0, 0, 2, 8, '', '', 'Whilst out fishing, the postman sails past an island that is home to a strange creature called the Drop Dragon. Whisked away from his normal life, he makes friends with the island''s inhabitants and together, they help to awaken the postman''s distant memories.', '', '', '', '', '2005-04-01 00:00:00', '21 x 16', '80', 1, 'ht_postmannthedropdragon_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(417, 0, 'The Buttons in the Dish', 94, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 10, '|10|', '', 'In the Takahashi family''s closet, there is a white plate on which the family keeps mislaid buttons. The buttons enjoy chatting with their past experiences and their future dreams, until they are returned to where they belong. Each button has its own storyÉ A storybook with delightful illustrations. ', '', '', '', '', '2007-10-01 00:00:00', '19 x 16', '102', 1, '112007buttonsontheplate_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2010-04-16 14:39:06', 62, 1),
(418, 0, 'Crane, Crane', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 230, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|10|', '', 'Every morning a little boy watches a crane on its way to work, lifting girders on a building site, helping move a sick elephant at the zoo, pulling out a car which has fallen into the river. A story which captures the romance of machines for small children.', '', '', '', '', '1991-11-01 00:00:00', '26 x 21', '32', 1, 'cranecrane_big.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(419, 0, 'My Fire Engine', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 230, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'A little boy imagines all the things he could do if he had his own fire engine. In addition to putting out fires, he could water people''s gardens, wash elephants, feed giraffes, rescue cats and retrieve children''s balloons. All the children who read this book will want their own fire engine!', '', '', '', '', '1993-12-01 00:00:00', '26 x 21', '32', 1, 'myfireengine_big.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(420, 17, 'The Beginning of the Journey', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'Sangoro the black cat is looking for treasure. He asks Ken to help him and they set off on an adventure together.', 'Award', '1995 AKAITORI AWARD FOR ILLUSTRATIONS\r\n1995 ROBO-NO-ISHI AWARD', '', '', '1994-07-01 00:00:00', '21 x 15', '140', 2, 'stbcbeginningofthejourney_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 17:10:32', 62, 1),
(421, 17, 'En Route to the Kirara Ocean', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 230, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'To save the black-tailed gulls from a fatal disease, Sangoro heads for a dangerous ocean to hunt for a wonder drug: a glass shell.', '', '', '', '', '1994-07-01 00:00:00', '21 x 15', '140', 2, 'stbcerttko_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(422, 17, 'Wildcat-bird Island', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 230, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'There is a kareha-fever epidemic on Wildcat-bird Island, where a longstanding feud exists between the black-tailed gulls and the wildcat-birds. Sangoro risks his life trying to save the lives of the wildcat-birds.', '', '', '', '', '1994-09-01 00:00:00', '21 x 15', '140', 2, 'stbcwcbi_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(423, 17, 'The Black Pirate Ship', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 230, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'Sangoro, who has gone to New Moon Island on business, is targeted by a pirate ship and seriously wounded. This is the adventure of Ikamal and Sangoro.', '', '', '', '', '1994-09-01 00:00:00', '21 x 15', '140', 2, 'stbctbpship_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(424, 17, 'The Lighthouse in the Fog', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 230, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'Sangoro is lost in fog at sea. He arrives at a strange island, the home of Kai, the lighthouse keeper. Sangoro and Kai develop a deep friendship but Kai is not what he seemsÉ', '', '', '', '', '1994-12-01 00:00:00', '21 x 15', '140', 2, 'stbctlinthefog_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(425, 18, 'The Blue Joker', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 230, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'Ikamal, who is worried about Sangoro who is on a dangerous mission, finally manages to get hold of a boat, ''the Dolphin'', and sets out to find him. ', '', '', '', '', '1996-01-01 00:00:00', '21 x 15', '135', 2, 'stbctjcthebluejoker_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(426, 18, 'Ken and Milly', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 230, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'Ken and his cousin Milly are adrift in a boat at sea at night and rapidly being swept away by the tide when Ken is suddenly reunited with Sangoro, the black cat. (To be continued!)', '', '', '', '', '1996-03-01 00:00:00', '21 x 15', '135', 2, 'stbctjckenandmilly_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(427, 18, 'Overcoming the Blaze', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 230, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'Sangoro is visiting Kaigara Island when he finds himself caught up in a power struggle over who will succeed an elder leader who has met with an untimely death. ', '', '', '', '', '1996-04-01 00:00:00', '21 x 15', '135', 2, 'stbctjcothebraze_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(428, 18, 'Golden Waves, Silver Winds', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 230, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', '(Special edition containing 3 separate stories) Sangoro, on his boat, ''Marin'', visits a series of islands where he encounters many interesting characters and has many exciting experiences. ', '', '', '', '', '1996-04-01 00:00:00', '21 x 15', '135', 2, 'stbctjcgwsw_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(429, 18, 'The Last Letter', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 230, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'To return to his past and save a young girl to whom he owes his life, Sangoro heads for the northern ocean of Block which, in order to avoid a curse, he must not cross more than three times.', '', '', '', '', '1996-04-01 00:00:00', '21 x 15', '135', 2, 'stbctjcthelastletter_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(430, 0, 'Pin Pon Bus', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 92, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|8|11|', '', 'Pin Pon Bus and his driver are a busy bus service; from terminal to countryside, they call at the supermarket, the school and the hospital; they pick up children and pets, wait for late passengers and help with left luggage. Soon night falls. Who will they pick up on their way back home?', '', '', '', '', '1996-09-01 00:00:00', '21 x 26', '32', 1, 'pinponbus_big.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-04 14:44:26', 62, 1),
(431, 0, 'Hello, Hello', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 235, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|13|', '', 'Not so long ago people used to write letters to communicate with one another. But now we have the telephone! A girl hippo rings her grandma to say "thank you" for present, a cow phones the fire brigade, a horse calls the police after a robbery, a pig orders a pizza... How useful the telephone is!', '', '', '', '', '2000-08-01 00:00:00', '21 x 22', '32', 1, 'hellohello_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-02 07:22:33', 62, 1),
(432, 0, 'Pin Pon Bus Goes to the Seaside', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 92, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|8|', '', 'Pin Pon Bus takes a little boy to the seaside; riding through the city streets, over a level crossing, past a fire station and road works, to leave the city behind. Up a hill, through a tunnel, there''s the sea! Last stop is the beach. Off we get! ', '', '', '', '', '2004-06-01 00:00:00', '21 x 26', '32', 1, 'pinponbusgoesto_big.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-04 14:46:44', 62, 1),
(433, 0, 'On the Road with the Home Delivery Service', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 92, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|8|11|', '', 'The story traces the journey of a box of apples, from Grandad''s apple orchard through the home delivery service. What a journey! Onto small trucks, through sorting centres, onto larger trucks, travelling on the motorways and through the night until the apples are safely delivered to his city grandchildren.', '', '', '', '', '2005-12-01 00:00:00', '21x 26', '32', 1, 'ontheroadwithhomedelivery_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-04 15:05:30', 62, 1),
(434, 0, 'Hurrah for the Police Car!', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 92, 0, 0, 0, 1, 3, '|8|11|', '', 'The police car on patrol around town is full of enthusiasm, cautioning a dangerous car, giving a passenger directions and taking a lost dog to his owner. It even chases and catches a gang of jewellery store robbers, cooperating with the other police cars.', '', '', '', '', '2007-04-01 00:00:00', '21 x 26', '32', 1, '072007hurrahforthepolicecar_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-04 15:19:01', 62, 1),
(647, 46, 'Morning and Night, Private Eye', 302, 0, 0, 0, '', 303, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '|11|', '', 'Milky Sugiyama and his children are invited to a friend''s restaurant by Captain Stuborn. But when he arrives, the chef has been knocked out, and his wallet stolen… This time it is Milky''s son, Takashi, who gives his father the hint he needs. Will father and son solve the crime? The boaok contains four stories.', '', '', '', '', '2008-03-01 00:00:00', '22×16', '152', 3, '345300_Morning_and_Night_Private_Eye.jpg', '2009-11-01 23:42:30', 62, '2011-03-04 16:47:32', 62, 1),
(436, 0, 'Scoop Scoop! Digger', 95, 1, 0, 0, '', 92, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|8|', '', 'A week in the life of a digger holds a lot of different jobs and challenges. Planting trees, travelling up mountains to help prevent avalanches, working on construction sitesÉ Then Sunday comes around, and it''s time for a hard-earned rest. ', '', '', '', '', '2008-04-01 00:00:00', '21 x 26', '32', 1, '052008scoop_scoop_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-04 15:22:26', 62, 1),
(437, 0, 'The Forest Kingdom', 96, 1, 0, 0, '', 184, 0, 0, 0, 3, 12, '', '', 'Veterinary surgeon and naturalist Taketazu writes about his post - war childhood adventures in the northen Kyushu countryside. Includes stories about fishing for bullfrogs at a haunted pond, collecting sumac berries to make candles, digging yams and catching a Daurian redstart.', '', '', '', '', '1996-01-01 00:00:00', '21 x 16', '216', 5, 'theforestkingdom_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(438, 0, 'The Sparrow Who Joined the Family', 96, 1, 0, 0, '', 179, 0, 0, 0, 3, 9, '|8|20|', '', 'An elderly Hokkaido vet who devotes much time and effort to the treatment of injured wild creatures describes how a sparrow whose life he saved rejected all attempts to be returned to the wild and became a member of his family.', 'Award', '1998 THE SANKEI AWARD FOR CHILDREN''S BOOKS & PUBLICATIONS', '', '', '1997-09-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '174', 6, 'thesparrowwjtf_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 13:59:52', 62, 1),
(439, 0, 'The Gift of Helen the Fox Cub', 96, 1, 0, 0, '', 179, 0, 0, 0, 3, 9, '|8|20|10|', '', 'Account by a retired Hokkaido vet of his attempts to raise a blind and deaf fox cub which he found abandoned at the side of the road. The young animal eventually died, but its gentle character left such a lasting impression on the author and his wife that this book is the result.', '', '', '', '', '1999-05-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '174', 6, 'thegiftofhelentfc_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 14:15:14', 62, 1),
(440, 0, 'The Wild Animal Clinic A Photographic Record', 96, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 3, 9, '|10|20|', '', 'The author who owns a wild animal clinic in Hokkaido has put together a collection of around 150 photographs spanning 30 years of contact with wild animals. A vibrant depiction of the daily activities of the animals and the staff. All aspects of animal care are detailed in this heart - warming book.', '', '', '', '', '2004-01-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '216', 5, 'thewildanimalclinicapr_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(441, 0, 'The Animal Trial - the Lion''s Job', 96, 1, 0, 0, '', 156, 0, 0, 0, 3, 6, '|10|', '', 'Set in the Tanzanian grasslands. The lion, which had attacked a gnu, is put on trial. After hearing accounts from 8 witnesses, the jury reaches a verdict. A picture book showing us how life really is in the animal world.', '', '', '', '', '2004-08-01 00:00:00', '24 x 29', '32', 1, 'theanimaltrialtlj_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(442, 0, 'The Animal Court Are the Cranes Corrupt Landlords?', 96, 1, 0, 0, '', 156, 0, 0, 0, 3, 6, '|11|', '', 'The animal court gathers to hear the case of the cranes versus the daces. The cranes eat the daces, treating their flesh as an annual stipend or tax, much to the dace''s dislike. The court must decide who is right in this thought provoking picture book. ', '', '', '', '', '2006-04-01 00:00:00', '24 x 29', '32', 1, 'theanimalcourtatccl_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 14:33:34', 62, 1);
INSERT INTO `jos_publications_titles_2011-08-26` (`id`, `series_id`, `title`, `author_id`, `author_type`, `author2_id`, `author2_type`, `author_ext`, `illustrator_id`, `illustrator2_id`, `photographer_id`, `photographer2_id`, `cat_id`, `age_group_id`, `country_id`, `country_ext`, `synopsis`, `sub1_title`, `sub1_text`, `sub2_title`, `sub2_text`, `publication_year`, `book_size`, `pages`, `book_colour`, `imageurl`, `created`, `created_by`, `modified`, `modified_by`, `published`) VALUES
(443, 0, 'The Hedgehog and the Gold Coin', 97, 1, 75, 6, '', 218, 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, '|10|29|', '', 'An hedgehog discovers a gold coin in the road. He decides to use it to buy some mushrooms, but the squirrel gives him them and refuses the money. The same thing happens when he tries to buy something. The hedgehog decides to return the coin. Perhaps it will be of use to someone else.', 'Award', '2004 THE SANKEI AWARD FOR CHILDREN''S BOOKS & PUBLICATIONS ', '', '', '2003-11-01 00:00:00', '27 x 21', '32', 1, 'hedgehognthegoldcoin_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2010-12-08 22:44:48', 62, 1),
(444, 0, 'Everyone''s a Skeleton', 98, 1, 0, 0, '', 239, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'This colourful and thought-provoking picture book introduces readers to a number of skeletons. They play skipping, play on the slide, play on the climbing frame and eat ice cream before it is time to go home; but is there more to these skeletons than meets the eye?', '', '', '', '', '2006-03-01 00:00:00', '21 x 21', '29', 1, 'everyonesaskeleton_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(445, 0, 'Two Trees', 99, 3, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 260, 0, 1, 6, '', '', 'Two trees are growing close together and, at any time of the year, if you listen to the conversation between these two tree friends, you can learn the way to find happiness. A heart warming photographic picture book. ', '', '', '', '', '2004-06-01 00:00:00', '23 x 24', '36', 1, 'twotrees_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(446, 0, 'Dr Mimizu and the Living Earth', 100, 1, 0, 0, '', 243, 0, 0, 0, 3, 10, '', '', 'Dr Mimizu is healthy and producing delicious vegetables from the ''Living Earth''. This is a story about Dr Mimizu''s continuing demands for environmentally friendly farming methods.', '', '', '', '', '2004-06-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '173', 2, 'drmimizundalivingearth_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(447, 0, 'Fukimanbuku the Girl and the Flowers', 101, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, '', '', 'Fuki, a village girl, falls asleep on a hillside. She dreams she is a tiny underground shoot. Through her dream she senses the secret of life, the warmth of Mother Earth. The artist-author is a farmer in the hills near Tokyo.', '', '', '', '', '1973-04-01 00:00:00', '25 x 29', '35', 1, 'st_fukimanbuku_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(448, 0, 'Drop a Stone and Forget', 101, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, '', '', 'It doesn''t matter what the old man does, he''s always making mistakes. Since he got up this morning he hasn''t stopped doing silly things like breaking eggs. His wife sees what he''s doing andÉ. A portrayal of an old couple''s beautiful heart-warming way of life.', '', '', '', '', '1980-06-01 00:00:00', '23 x 25', '52', 1, 'st_dropstonenforget_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(449, 0, 'Ball in the Grass', 101, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, '|10|', '', 'What happens to the ball after it whizzes into the thick grass? Imaginative paintings done in bright primary colours take the reader with the ball on its journey. The book contains simple text.', '', '', '', '', '1982-12-01 00:00:00', '25 x 28', '36', 1, 'st_ballinthegrass_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 14:06:17', 62, 1),
(450, 0, 'Fly, Grasshopper!', 101, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, '|9|10|11|', '', 'Bold and powerful pictures tell the story of a brave little grasshopper who, sick of spending everyday cringing in the grass in fear of his enemies, decides to come out into a sun.', 'Award', '1989 BOLOGNA INTERNATIONAL BOOK FAIR (Nominated for Graphic Prize)\r\n1988 NIPPON PRIZE FOR PICTURE BOOKS (Grand Prix)\r\n1989 SHOGAKUKAN AWARD FOR ILLUSTRATIONS FOR CHILDREN', '', '', '1988-07-01 00:00:00', '24 x 30', '36', 1, 'flygrasshopper_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 23:32:47', 62, 1),
(451, 0, 'Unknown Town', 101, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, '|10|', '', 'A boy gets on an empty bus, which takes him to a strange town. Birds grow from the ground, and buildings are made of vegetables. In a hamburger shop, a hamburger is selling potted plants of cats. He eventually finds a restaurant, but a dandelion begins to eat him!', '', '', '', '', '2006-07-01 00:00:00', '26 x 29', '32', 1, 'unknowntown_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(452, 0, 'The Sand Castle', 102, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'A boy making a sand castle on the beach is drawn into a fantasy world, in which people and objects materialize from the sand. He meets the sand king. When the tide comes in, the castle is washed away. But the boy is left with the magic rainbow shell that he received from the king.', '', '', '', '', '2001-07-01 00:00:00', '26 x 22', '40', 1, 'st_sandcastle_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(453, 0, 'Lancelot and Pablo', 102, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, '', '', 'Lancelot the robot and Pablo the teddy bear have a very beautiful friendship. When scatterbrain Lancelot forgets a promise, kind-hearted Teddy always forgives him. You see, Teddy understands Lancelot''s nature. This charming story shows what happens when the two friends make an agreement to go fishing on Soda pond.', '', '', '', '', '2003-10-01 00:00:00', '26 x 19', '32', 1, 'st_lancelotandpablo_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(454, 0, 'Lancelot Goes Mushrooming', 102, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, '', '', 'Lancelot invites Monja the cat to go looking for wild mushrooms with him and together they discover a strange world in which the mushroom kings rules his nation. Upon returning Lancelot accidentally grows massive mushrooms that grow through his roof. Together with his friends, they gorge on the delicious mushrooms.', '', '', '', '', '2004-10-01 00:00:00', '26 x 19', '32', 1, 'st_lancelotgoesmushrooming_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(455, 0, 'Lancelot and His Honey Cake', 102, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, '', '', 'Lancelot the robot has just made another robot called Jigo Jigo Pee. As he lost honey cakes that Lancelot wanted by accident, they decide to make a big one with Pablo''s honey, Monja''s flour and Ptera the Dinosaur''s egg by using a small volcano. Can they make a delicious cake?', '', '', '', '', '2005-10-01 00:00:00', '26 x 19', '32', 1, 'st_lancelotandhishoneycake_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(456, 0, 'The Adventure of the Cactus Kid', 102, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 15, '', '', 'An updated version of an enduringly popular story first published in 1988, this vividly illustrated book tells of a young cactus boy who comes to life during the full moon. He travels to the city, whereupon he and a bearded old man set off for the land of the cactus people in an old car. ', '', '', '', '', '2006-12-01 00:00:00', '19 x 14', '80', 3, 'st_adventureofcactuskid_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(457, 0, 'Where Are You Going, Snowman?', 102, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 8, '', '', 'A snowman borrows a pair of skis, but being just a beginner, he crashes into a bear by mistake. When the huge angry bear begins to chase him, the snowman embarks on an exciting journey over mountains and deserts, though the city and the sky, and even into a ski race and a doughnut shop. ', '', '', '', '', '2007-10-01 00:00:00', '21 x 16', '96', 1, '112007wrugoingsnowman_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(458, 19, 'Suzuna, The Little Mountain Goddess', 103, 1, 0, 0, '', 175, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'Suzuna wants to independently rule the mountains like her father. One day, she manages to make him promise that if she succeeds in colouring all the trees in the mountains with autumnal tints, her wish will be granted.', 'Award', '1997 AKAITORI AWARD FOR ILLUSTRATIONS\r\n1997 NIIMI NANKICHI AWARD', '', '', '1996-03-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '134', 2, 'suzunatlmg_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 17:13:35', 62, 1),
(459, 19, 'The Big Catfish in Suzuna Marsh', 103, 1, 0, 0, '', 175, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'Suzuna, the new goddess of Mount Suzuna, initially thinks about bringing back the water into the marsh as it has run dry, but she doesn''t want to invoke the wrath of the big catfish.', '', '', '', '', '1996-03-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '134', 2, 'suzunatbcim_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(460, 19, 'The Evening of the Big Cloud Payday', 103, 1, 0, 0, '', 175, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'It''s New Year''s Eve and the Big Cloud Payday is an extremely busy time for the mountain gods, but somebody has stolen the main attraction of the mountain, the thousand-year-old cherry tree.', '', '', '', '', '1996-09-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '134', 2, 'suzunateotbcp_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(461, 19, 'The Devil of Darkness Valley', 103, 1, 0, 0, '', 175, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '', '', 'Forgetting the advice of her father, Suzuna has been tricked by the Devil of Darkness Valley in the West. If she is unable to solve the Devil''s riddle, she may lose Mount Suzuna. ', '', '', '', '', '1996-11-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '134', 2, 'suzunatdodv_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(462, 0, 'Bokko', 103, 1, 0, 0, '', 182, 0, 0, 0, 2, 11, '', '', 'When Shigeru attends his grandmother''s funeral he meets a strange boy who tells him ''Don''t worry. I''ll look after you.'' Shigeru does not understand. Only later when he learns that he will live at his grandmother''s house that he realises something strange is happening.', '', '', '', '', '1998-05-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '230', 2, 'bokko_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(463, 0, 'The Nature God of the Skies', 103, 1, 0, 0, '', 171, 0, 0, 0, 2, 11, '', '', 'We don''t know the name of the god who has started to live in Satoko''s bedroom, or where he comes from.', 'Award', '2001 THE SANKEI AWARD FOR CHILDREN''S BOOKS & PUBLICATIONS', '', '', '2000-06-01 00:00:00', '21 x 16', '286', 2, 'thenaturegodoftheskis_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(464, 20, 'The Secret Lake in the Looking Glass', 103, 1, 0, 0, '', 214, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '|8|11|', '', 'This is the third story about the three Shinoda children, Yui, Takumi and Moe, whose mother and relations are all foxes! In this installment, their grandmother sends them an old looking glass, which leads to all kinds of mysteries, and the legend of a kappa water sprite!', '', '', '', '', '2000-06-01 00:00:00', '20 x 14', '238-366', 2, 'stslitglass_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2010-09-05 04:57:59', 62, 1),
(465, 0, 'God of the Shrine', 103, 1, 0, 0, '', 192, 0, 0, 0, 2, 11, '', '', 'Yuhei and his friends have found the shrine of the gods, the ''Hokora''. They make many wishes which all cometrue, but for some reason bad things also happen. ', '', '', '', '', '2002-01-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '210', 2, 'godoftheshrine_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(466, 20, 'The Little Dragon and the Magic Fruit', 103, 1, 0, 0, '', 214, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '|8|11|', '', 'In Japanese folklore, the fox possesses the power to turn itself into a human. This story mixes folklore, fantasy and humour to introduce a family with a secret -  the mother is a fox in human disguise. Being a fox, she and her many relatives can do many magic tricks.', '', '', '', '', '2003-07-01 00:00:00', '20 x 14', '238-367', 2, 'stldatmf_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2010-09-05 04:57:26', 62, 1),
(467, 20, 'Tree Words and Stone Seals', 103, 1, 0, 0, '', 214, 0, 0, 0, 2, 9, '|8|11|', '', 'Three children are descended from foxes, and possess supernatural powers. Sent on a mission to help the people of the mountain who have been turned to stone, they team up and use their combined skills to find the golden acorn, crossing dimensions and encountering untold adventure.', '', '', '', '', '2004-09-01 00:00:00', '20 x 14', '238-368', 2, 'stwass_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2010-09-05 04:57:43', 62, 1),
(468, 0, 'Is That So? -  A Record of My Experiences', 103, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 15, '', '', '''People tend to think that a writer of fairy tales should be an innocent person and a perfect parent, but apparently I am notÉ'' This is a collection of essays by the children''s storywriter. She depicts her everyday life with her two sons, her work and her memories of childhood humorously. Full of laughs, and occasional sentimentalisms. ', '', '', '', '', '2007-05-01 00:00:00', '14 x 20', '116', 2, '112007isthatso_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(469, 0, 'Going to the Sea in Summer', 104, 1, 0, 0, '', 203, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'It''s the hottest summer in centuries--- even the rocks are perspiring. Under the burning sun, the bear, fox and raccoon wonder what to do. When the bear shouts out '' We''re going to the sea!'', all the animals big and small to head for the ocean. ', '', '', '', '', '1997-05-01 00:00:00', '25x 21', '32', 1, 'going2thecinsummer_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(470, 10, 'The Fox''s Friend-shop', 104, 1, 0, 0, '', 165, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|10|11|', '', 'A crafty fox sets up an one-man business selling friendship at an hourly rate to animals of the forest. However, he changes his attitude after an encounter with a kind-hearted card-playing wolf who teaches him that true friends cannot be bought with money.', '', '', '', '', '1998-01-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'waf_foxsfriendshop_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-04 16:41:40', 62, 1),
(471, 10, 'Will My Friend Come?', 104, 1, 0, 0, '', 165, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|10|11|', '', 'A wolf tries to console himself when his friend the fox fails to show on his birthday. Why does he feel so lonely? Perhaps it''s because he has a heart. He wonders if it wouldn''t be better throw his heart away. Luckily, the arrival of the fox makes him feel the joy of heart-to-heart friendship.', '', '', '', '', '1999-02-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'waf_willmyfriendcome_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-04 16:42:32', 62, 1),
(472, 10, 'Always Friends', 104, 1, 0, 0, '', 165, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|10|', '', 'The wolf and the little fox are playmates. But, one day the wolf brusquely tells the fox to go home. The fox is sad because he thinks that the wolf has made friends with someone else. But, actually, the wolf is secretly nursing an injured bear.', '', '', '', '', '2000-10-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'waf_alwaysfriends_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-04 16:39:09', 62, 1),
(473, 10, 'Sorry, Friend', 104, 1, 0, 0, '', 165, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|10|', '', 'The wolf and the fox are friends, but whatever the game - darts, cup and ball, or cards - the skillful fox always wins. In a fit of temper the wolf kicks the poor fox out of his house. Later he regrets his bad behavior. The rest of the story shows how the two friends make up.', '', '', '', '', '2001-03-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'waf_sorryfriend_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-04 16:40:22', 62, 1),
(474, 10, 'Any Unwanted Friends?', 104, 1, 0, 0, '', 165, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'The wild boar and the stoat are having an argument over which one of them is the boss. The boar is behaving very badly. Nearby, the fox and the wolf wonder how they can teach the boar a lesson. The story tells how the boar sells his friend the stoat, but then later comes to regret his arrogance.', '', '', '', '', '2002-02-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'waf_anyunwantedfriends_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-04 16:39:40', 62, 1),
(475, 10, 'Thank You, Friend !', 104, 1, 0, 0, '', 165, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|11|', '', 'After boasting about his fishing exploits, the wolf takes his friend the fox to the seaside. However, once there, it''s the fox that catches all the fish. This makes the proud wolf irritated and angry. But the two friends later make it up, and the story finishes with a joyful barbecue on the beach.', '', '', '', '', '2003-06-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'waf_thankyoufriend_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-04 16:40:44', 62, 1),
(476, 10, 'That Chap is Also My Friend', 104, 1, 0, 0, '', 165, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|10|', '', '"The wolf is my friend, but how about the snake?" thinks the fox. Just before hybernation, the fox''s fears make him neglect saying "hello" to the snake. As he enjoys the winter with his friends, he begins to feel guilty about this. Upon awakening from a dream of loneliness, the snake is pleased to make friends with the fox.', '', '', '', '', '2004-10-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'waf_chapisalsomyfriend_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-04 16:41:10', 62, 1),
(477, 10, 'The Friendship Chant', 104, 1, 0, 0, '', 165, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'The importance of good friendship is emphasized by the friendship chant introduced in this volume. The fox and the wolf are great friends, but a misunderstanding causes them to fall out. Neither of them is able to apologise, so the situation continues, until they make up by placing snails on each other''s noses.', '', '', '', '', '2006-11-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '48', 1, 'waf_friendshipchant_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-04 16:20:32', 62, 1),
(478, 0, 'The Sacred Tree', 105, 1, 0, 0, '', 166, 0, 0, 0, 2, 12, '', '', 'Little is known about the inhabitants of Naira, a planet colonized by people from Earth, except that their civilization came to swift and sudden end... A powerful story which weaves science fiction with animism, myth and strong moral undertones.', '', '', '', '', '1989-05-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '334-359', 2, 'thesacredtree_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(479, 23, 'Guardian of the Spirit', 105, 1, 0, 0, '', 166, 0, 0, 0, 2, 12, '|22|8|2|23|15|5|11|13|', '', 'Once every hundred years an egg containing a sacred spirit is implanted into the breast of an inhabitant of Sagu. If the egg is safely hatched, the land will be free of famines and natural disasters for the next century. This fantasy novel relates how a prince receives the egg, attempts to protect it from those who seek to destroy it.', 'Award', '1996 NOMA NEWCOMER PRIZE FOR JUVENILE LITERATURE\r\n1997 THE SANKEI AWARD FOR CHILDREN''S BOOKS & PUBLICATIONS\r\n2001 ROBO-NO-ISHI AWARD', 'Broadcast of Guardian of the Spirit animated series', 'The Japanese public broadcaster NHK has begun transmission of an animated version of Guardian of the Sacred Spirit. The fantasy world of Nahoko Uehashi''s story has been brought to the screen by Production I.G., who are active around the world, producing programmes such as ''Innocence'', and the animation director Kenji Kamiyama, who has directed key Japanese works such as ''Ghost in the Shell''.', '1996-07-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '284-358', 2, 'gothesacredspirit_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-12-03 01:08:26', 62, 1),
(480, 23, 'Guardian of the Dark', 105, 1, 0, 0, '', 166, 0, 0, 0, 2, 12, '|8|23|15|5|11|', '', 'Balsa, a woman warrior, returns to the kingdom of her birth, from where, as a child, she was forced to flee after her father was killed by the king. Her mission is to clear the name of Jiguro, a friend of her father, who fell into disgrace as a result of helping her.', 'Award', '2000 JAPANESE ASSOCIATION OF WRITERS FOR CHILDREN PRIZE\r\n2001 ROBO-NO-ISHI AWARD', '', '', '1999-01-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '284-359', 2, 'gothedark_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-12-03 01:09:06', 62, 1),
(481, 23, 'Guardian of the Dream', 105, 1, 0, 0, '', 166, 0, 0, 0, 2, 12, '|8|15|5|11|', '', 'Mythological adventure epic revolving around a magical flower which tempts people to escape the painful reality of human existence into a world of dream. How can Balsa the woman warrior save a young apothecary who in challenging the flower has been robbed of his own humanity?', 'Award', '2001 ROBO-NO-ISHI AWARD', '', '', '2000-05-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '284-360', 2, 'gothedream_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2010-05-11 09:21:55', 62, 1),
(482, 24, 'Traveller of the Void', 105, 1, 0, 0, '', 226, 0, 0, 0, 2, 12, '|11|', '', 'A teenage crown prince travels across the sea to a kingdom with his tutor to attend the coronation of a king. However, a shadow is cast over the occasion when the new king is wounded. The prince finds himself in a dangerous situation. ', '', '', '', '', '2001-07-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '334-357', 2, 'travellerofthevoid_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(483, 23, 'Guardian of the Awful God Volume 2: Return from the Hard Journey', 105, 1, 0, 0, '', 166, 0, 0, 0, 2, 12, '|8|11|', '', 'Asra, the mysterious child that Balsa so impulsively helped, is slowly revealing her dark secret. Her special powers are beginning to make themselves felt in the Kingdom of Rota, which has been split into two, as north clashes with south. Whilst fearful of the powers she possesses, Asra begins to draw closer to the awful god…All the while, Shihana, an undercover agent from the Kingdom of Rota, is in hot pursuit of Balsa.  Will Balsa manage to protect Asra from the forces that threaten here, both from without and within? ', 'Award', '2003 SHOGAKUKAN CULTURAL PRIZE IN PUBLISHING FOR CHILDREN''S BOOKS', '', '', '2003-01-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '284-361', 2, 'gotagv2ga_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2010-03-16 19:02:40', 62, 1),
(484, 24, 'Traveller of the Blue Road', 105, 1, 0, 0, '', 226, 0, 0, 0, 2, 12, '|11|', '', 'Chagum, the Crown Prince of the Kingdom of Shin-Yogo, sets out on a perilous journey to protect his homeland. A tantalizing sword and sorcery style adventure, this is the second volume in Nahoko Uehashi''s ''Traveller'' series..', '', '', '', '', '2005-04-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '334-358', 2, 'travelleroftheblueroad_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(485, 23, 'Guardian of Heaven and Earth - Part 1', 105, 1, 0, 0, '', 166, 0, 0, 0, 2, 12, '', '', 'Balsa, a female warrior, sets out for the Kingdom of Lota in an attempt to rescue Chagum, the Crown Prince of Shin-Yogo, hitherto believed dead. She finds he is alive, but in order to protect his homeland at the risk of ruin, he decides to carry on with his dangerous quest.', '', '', '', '', '2007-01-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '350', 2, 'gohaevenandearth1_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(486, 23, 'Guardian of Heaven and Earth - Part 2', 105, 1, 0, 0, '', 166, 0, 0, 0, 2, 12, '', '', 'Chagum, Prince of Shin-Yogo and Balsa the female warrior head for the Kingdom of Kambal. Chagum intends to persuade the king of Kambal to forge an alliance with the Kingdom of Lota and put down the enormous influence of their neighbour nation Talsh, which is menacing his homeland of Shin-Yogo.', '', '', '', '', '2007-01-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '310', 2, '072007gohaevenandearth2_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(487, 23, 'Guardian of Heaven and Earth - Part 3', 105, 1, 0, 0, '', 166, 0, 0, 0, 2, 12, '', '', 'Chagum, Prince of Shin-Yogo finally returns to his homeland with the help of Balsa. The attack by the Talsh has already started, taking many civilian lives. He makes up his mind to lead the nation as Emperor, while Balsa finds her old partner Tanda injured by the war. This is the concluding volume in the trilogy.', '', '', '', '', '2007-02-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '366', 2, '072007gohaevenandearth3_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(488, 25, 'The Wanderer', 105, 1, 0, 0, '', 166, 0, 0, 0, 2, 12, '', '', 'Tanda, a sensitive eleven-year-old boy, adores Balsa, who is drifting about with her stepfather, fleeing from a plot against them. They try to find out about a curse in the village and discover the painful secret of a dead wastrelÉ A collection of prequel stories to the popular ''MORIBITO (Guardian)'' series.', '', '', '', '', '2008-04-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '366', 2, '052008guardian_short_story_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(489, 0, 'The Tale of Cherry the Pig', 106, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, '|13|', '', 'Cherry is a pig who loves making cakes and then eating them with her afternoon tea. This story is about how a chance comment by a group of rats gives her the idea of entering a cake-making contest. Only later does she learn that the mice had not intended their comment as a compliment at all.', '', '', '', '', '2002-09-01 00:00:00', '26 x 20', '32', 1, 'taleofcherrythepig_big.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(490, 0, 'Little Rabbit Pipin''s Birthday', 106, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, '', '', 'Pipin has long ears with which he listens to what is going on. Each sound gives him a different sort of feeling. But it''s all very difficult to explain to his friends. Then one day, on Pipin''s birthday, he goes on a country walk and hears a very strange sound. What can it be?', '', '', '', '', '2003-10-01 00:00:00', '26 x 20', '32', 1, 'littlerabbitpipinsbirthday_big.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(491, 0, 'Buzzy the Honeybee', 106, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'Inspired by the author''s carefree childhood days, this beautifully illustrated story book tells of Buzzy, a young honeybee who spends each day playing with her best friend, Coaty the ladybird. One day, adventure ensues when she takes a nap, and ends up in a human being''s house - will she get out in one piece?', '', '', '', '', '2006-10-01 00:00:00', '21 x 18', '28', 1, 'buzzythehoneybee_big.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(492, 0, 'Mr Pencil', 107, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 3, '', '', 'I have noticed that my pencil did all my homework for me. I might think I''m a genius but it was my pencil that did it. This story is about the friendship between my very curious pencil and me.', '', '', '', '', '2004-08-01 00:00:00', '21 x 19', '32', 1, 'mrpencil_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(493, 0, 'The Wild Cooking Park', 107, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 10, '', '', 'The story begins with an ad posted through the letterbox. At first it is thought to be simply advertising a place where you can "eat as much as you like". But completely unexpected things begin to happen. ', '', '', '', '', '2005-11-01 00:00:00', '20 x 15', '80', 1, 'wildcookingpark_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(494, 0, 'My Dog Vamos', 108, 1, 0, 0, '', 235, 0, 0, 0, 2, 13, '', '', 'A boy in a seaside town receives a dog from Spain for his birthday. His story, which is told in the first person, follows the development of his feelings towards his pet: his frustrations, anxieties, joys... and, most of all, his love for the animal. Young readers will also be able to identify with the boy''s thoughts.', '', '', '', '', '2003-05-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '118', 2, 'mydogvamos_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(495, 0, 'Hiro the Pirate', 109, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 8, '', '', 'Hiro wets his bed at night, and when his sheet is hung out the blot resembles a skull and crossbones flying over pirate ship. So the fish mistake him for the pirate captain and invite him into the sea, where he heals sick fish and fights a shark.', '', '', '', '', '1970-04-01 00:00:00', '23 x 21', '104', 1, 'sc_hirothepirate_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(496, 0, 'In a Balloon over Eyelash Ocean', 109, 1, 0, 0, '', 229, 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, '|11|', '', 'Mortified after unjustly losing in a fight with a classmate, the little boy of the story is left sulking in the playground. Through his tears, the sky becomes a sea of rainbow waves as in his imagination he plots revenge.', 'Award', '1984 BOLOGNA INTERNATIONAL BOOK FAIR (Nominated for Graphic Prize)\r\n1983 NIPPON PRIZE FOR PICTURE BOOKS (Grand Prix)', '', '', '1983-01-01 00:00:00', '26 x 21', '32', 1, 'inaballooneyelashocean_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2008-10-18 17:13:07', 62, 1),
(497, 0, 'I''ll Give You the Sea', 109, 1, 0, 0, '', 202, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'It''s the hottest summer in centuries--- even the rocks are perspiring. Under the burning sun, the bear, fox and raccoon wonder what to do. When the bear shouts out '' We''re going to the sea!'', all the animals big and small to head for the ocean. ', '', '', '', '', '1999-06-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'illgiveuthesea_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(498, 0, 'Hit it over the Ocean', 109, 1, 0, 0, '', 229, 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, '', '', 'Determined to win a place in the local kids''baseball team, Wataru comes to the seashore to practice. There a mysterious boy who appears from the waves encourages him. Countless white balls are hurled from the waves.', '', '', '', '', '2000-07-01 00:00:00', '26 x 21', '32', 1, 'hs_hititoverdaocean_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(499, 0, 'Kindergarten Friends', 110, 1, 0, 0, '', 228, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'A little rabbit sets off for his first day at kindergarten. On the way he meets a squirrel, and later the two are joined by a fox, bear and elephant. Simple page cut-outs add to the fun in this delightful book about making friends.', '', '', '', '', '1992-07-01 00:00:00', 'Playing Book, 23 x 25', '32', 1, 'ky_kindergartenfriends_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(500, 0, 'What''s in Your Picnic Box?', 110, 1, 0, 0, '', 228, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'The rabbit and his kindergarten pals go on a picnic together. It''s time for lunch. The squirrel has a ''sun sandwich'', while the contents of the rabbit''s box look like two beautiful bunches of flowers.', '', '', '', '', '1992-11-01 00:00:00', 'Playing Book, 23 x 25', '38', 1, 'ky_whatsnurpicnicbox_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(501, 0, 'The Elephant''s Hat', 110, 1, 0, 0, '', 228, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'An elephant chases after his Tyrolean hat which has been blown off by the wind. During the search, he is joined by a rabbit, squirrel and fox, all of whom bear a partial resemblance to the missing article and are mistaken for it.', '', '', '', '', '1993-03-01 00:00:00', 'Playing Book, 23 x 25', '24', 1, 'ky_elephantshat_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(502, 0, 'Please Write Me', 110, 1, 0, 0, '', 212, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|10|', '', 'A tale of three cats: Seeing Kuro write a letter to Shamu and then waiting for a reply, Tora ponders the question `Why is receiving a letter such a wonderful thing?''', '', '', '', '', '2004-09-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'pleasewriteme_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(503, 0, 'I Want to Eat It All', 110, 1, 0, 0, '', 212, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'Tora finds a lump of bacon and takes it to the police. He can keep the bacon if the owner does not turn up within one day. He waits on the roof of the police box, dreaming of eating the whole thing, but eventually his friend Kuro comes to claim itÉ', '', '', '', '', '2006-09-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '32', 1, 'iwanttoeatitall_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(504, 11, 'A Rolling Rice Ball', 111, 2, 0, 0, '', 255, 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, '', '', 'This tale relates the story of how an old man''s rice ball rolls down a mousehole. It is the beginning of an adventure in which the man is invited by the mice into their underground home and presented with a chest of gold. Hearing of the episode, his neighbour tries to do the same, but...', '', '', '', '', '1967-06-01 00:00:00', '26 x 21', '32', 1, 'jpb_rollingriceball_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(505, 0, 'My Uncle', 112, 1, 0, 0, '', 244, 0, 0, 0, 2, 14, '', '', 'Ko reveals to me that, not only is his sister my mother in the parallel world we too find ourselves, but also that he is dead. Unravelling this story further, I realise that I am also not alive, as I am yet to be born. How can I feel all these sensations that are so clearly my mother? A dream-like moving story, painful yet full of hope.', '', '', '', '', '2004-10-01 00:00:00', '20 x 14', '87', 1, 'myuncle_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(506, 4, 'Heave-ho!', 113, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, '|10|11|', '', 'Working vehicles are very strong. The dump truck, wheel loader, forklift and power shovel dig and gather earth and sand, lift boxes and carry heavy things every day. Their shouts of encouragement echo around the construction site. "Heave-ho!" "Heave-ho!"', '', '', '', '', '2007-06-01 00:00:00', '18 x 18', '24', 1, '072007wv_heave-ho_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 16:53:10', 62, 1),
(507, 4, 'Can It Reach?', 113, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, '|10|11|', '', 'Working vehicles lift many objects and people to very high places. Can the crane lift steel frames and reach the top of the building? Can the lorry lift and install a road sign on a tall bar? Can the fire engine reach the fire in the building? Let''s see if they make it! ', '', '', '', '', '2007-06-01 00:00:00', '18 x 18', '24', 1, '072007wv_canitreach_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-09 10:09:17', 62, 1),
(508, 4, 'Leave It To Me!', 113, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, '|10|11|', '', 'With a little help from each other, working vehicles strive hard every day. You can hear their conversation at the construction site. "Please carry this earth for me, Mr. Dump Truck." "Leave it to me!" "I''m in trouble! Please carry me, Mr. Breakdown Lorry." "Leave it to me!"', '', '', '', '', '2007-06-01 00:00:00', '18 x 18', '24', 1, '072007wv_leaveit_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 16:49:47', 62, 1),
(509, 0, 'The Knock-Knock Door', 114, 1, 0, 0, '', 3, 0, 0, 0, 1, 2, '|10|', '', 'When we knock on the knock-knock door, all the toys come out to play. Then the time comes for them to go back. Goodbye everybody, see you again soon! The lyrics of the vocalist from Japanese band Kukikodan makes this book an ideal bed-time story. An audio CD containing two original music tracks is included. ', '', '', '', '', '2007-09-01 00:00:00', '26 x 20', '32', 1, '112007knock-knockdoor_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 14:39:53', 62, 1),
(510, 0, 'Little Dwellers in Ofuton Land', 115, 1, 0, 0, '', 163, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|10|', '', 'Hisako has a temperature and has to stay in her futon bed all day. It should have been a boring day for Hisako, but her futon bed has a secret which only children with a fever can see. ', '', '', '', '', '2005-11-01 00:00:00', '28 x 23', '34', 1, 'id_littledwellersofutonland_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(511, 0, 'Kids in N.Y.', 117, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'A look at the sights of exciting New York City through a child''s eyes. Double-page pictures feature everything from the Guggenheim Museum and Rockefeller Center to a street basketball court and coffee and bagels stand. There are also lots of useful colloquial phrases.', '', '', '', '', '2003-04-01 00:00:00', '30 x 22', '40', 1, 'kidsinny_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(512, 0, 'One Summer''s Day', 118, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|8|11|', '', '"It was a very hot summer''s day. I ran up to the mountain where a stag beetle lived. I remember the pure white sunlight and the smell of the green, green grassÉ"The pages of this book overflow with the sights and sounds of summer!', '', '', '', '', '2004-07-01 00:00:00', '26 x 22', '32', 1, 'onesummersday_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-12-03 01:15:05', 62, 1),
(513, 0, 'The Pencil Sumo Tournament', 119, 1, 0, 0, '', 259, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'On the desk in the middle of the night is the time and place for magic! The desk lamp provides the light for the ring where the sumo tournament will take place. Suddenly there is a huge commotion!', '', '', '', '', '2004-10-01 00:00:00', '19 x 25', '32', 1, 'pencilsumotournament_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(514, 0, 'I''m Not Giving Any Away!', 119, 1, 0, 0, '', 259, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'A greedy old woman loves nothing better than eating her favourite hand-baked treats. Although she has lots of animal friends who accompany her into the forest, she never gives any of her tasty goodies away. One day the animals tire of her meanness, and decide to her a lesson she won''t forgetÉ ', '', '', '', '', '2008-04-01 00:00:00', '25 x 19', '32', 1, '052008im_not_giving_any_away_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(515, 0, 'Sue''s Raincoat', 120, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'Since she cannot wait to wear her new lovely raincoat, Sue the rabbit goes to meet the rain. On the way she meets some friends to join her, and when they finally find it, it pours so strong and loud that they shelter under Sue''s raincoat and enjoy a ''festival of rain''.', '', '', '', '', '2007-06-01 00:00:00', '25 x 19', '32', 1, '072007suesraincoat_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(516, 0, 'Oola the Pony', 120, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'Oola takes white rabbit Sally with her everywhere, except for the bath. Even the dentist is not so bad if Sally is there -  after all, Oola has to be a good big sister and not cry. Illustrated with colourful collage, this will be a firm favourite of every child who has held on tight to something. ', '', '', '', '', '2008-05-01 00:00:00', '25 x 19', '32', 1, '052008oola_the_pony_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(517, 0, 'Our Morning', 121, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '', '', 'One day a mother boar tells her son that she''ll soon be having a baby. The little boar is excited and wonders what he can give, teach and share with his new brother or sister. When the morning of the birth finally arrives, the little boar visits his mother''s bed and finds three babies!', '', '', '', '', '2007-05-01 00:00:00', '26 x 19', '32', 1, '072007ourmorning_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(518, 0, 'The Robbers'' Great Escape!', 122, 1, 0, 0, '', 254, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|10|', '', 'Three robbers are fed up of living together in their tiny prison cell. They want to eat fluffy bread and pumpkin soup all day instead. So with their stripey uniforms, they disguise themselves as zebras and tigers, and manage to escape. Little do they expect that they will actually turn into wild animals! Imaginatively illustrated, this is a fantastically imaginative book. ', '', '', '', '', '2007-08-01 00:00:00', '26 x 22.', '32', 1, '112007robbersgreatescape_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 14:39:25', 62, 1),
(519, 0, '100 in Total', 123, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 4, '|18|12|8|2|3|15|26|28|11|14|', '', 'Count one hundred mice! The first one should be brown. Then count one hundred cats! How many of them are tabby? What about moles, sheep, birds, fish, elephants, children, ants, cars and housesÉ? A colourful and dynamic counting book full of the fun to be had with the counting process. ', '', '', '', '', '2008-01-01 00:00:00', '26 x 21', '24', 1, '100_in_total_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2011-03-04 15:53:29', 62, 1),
(520, 0, 'The Little Mermaid', 126, 2, 0, 0, 'based on an original story by H.C.Andersen', 178, 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, '|7|', '', 'Andersen''s tale of the mermaid who loves and loses a human prince and changes o foam. The polished text of Ayako Sono and the graceful pictures of Chihiro Iwasaki produce a magnigicent crystallisation of Andersen''s profound story.', '', '', '', '', '1967-12-01 00:00:00', '27 x 21', '32', 1, 'ci_littlemermaid_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 23:34:14', 62, 1),
(521, 0, 'Slowly with a Smile', 127, 1, 0, 0, '', 3, 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, '', '', 'People moving house, the sun moving across the sky, ants moving over the ground, a baby kangaroo travelling in its mother''s pouch, swallows preparing to migrate... Nothing in our world is ever still. Little Ayame-chan too is on the move. Slowly with a smile, she leaves her little playgroup to enter elementary school.', '', '', '', '', '1995-03-01 00:00:00', '26 x 21', '24', 1, 'ra_slowlywithasmile_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(522, 0, '1000 Winds, 1000 Cellos', 128, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 7, '|8|2|11|', '', 'A concert in aid of victims of the 1995 Great Hanshin Earthquake provided the inspiration for this picture book, which tells the story of two young participants and their teacher. A thousand individual cellos play a single tune.', '', '', '', '', '2000-11-01 00:00:00', '23 x 31', '32', 1, '1000winds1000cellos_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2010-09-05 04:51:31', 62, 1),
(523, 0, 'My Brother, Vincent', 128, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 10, '|10|11|', '', 'From the wheat fields of his childhood in Holland to the art dealers of Paris, this is the story of artist Vincent Van Gogh''s tragic yet spectacular life, as seen through the eyes of his younger brother Theo. With soft, sensitive illustrations to match its atmospheric prose, this book is guaranteed to touch the heart. ', '', '', '', '', '2008-03-01 00:00:00', '29 x 24', '40', 1, '052008my_brother_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-01 16:04:09', 62, 1),
(524, 0, 'Up to the Clouds', 129, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 14, '', '', 'A little boy standing in the open countryside under a large sky thinks how wonderful it would be if he could go up into the clouds. When he flaps his hands he mysteriously begins to rise - up and up until he is floating above the village houses, higher and higher until he is above the clouds.', '', '', '', '', '2002-03-01 00:00:00', '27 x 21', '32', 1, 'kk_uptotheclouds_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(525, 0, 'The Mississippi', 130, 10, 0, 0, '', 129, 0, 0, 0, 1, 14, '', '', 'This lavish volume contains images in pictures and words from a canoe trip made by a Japanese illustrator and his American companion down the Mississippi: ''Wilderness, pine trees... big lakes, small town, lonely people... big city, tall buildings, wind, always the wind...''', '', '', '', '', '1988-08-01 00:00:00', '26 x 37', '50', 1, 'kk_mississippi_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(526, 0, 'The Adventure of Chiyoro the Little Mouse', 131, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 10, '', '', 'The little mouse Chiyoro, running an errand to his cousin''s place for the first time, becomes friends with a ''magic stick'' . The stick rescues Chiyoro from a fierce and hungry snake by letting himself be swallowed by the snake, who gets horribly sick. How will Chiyoro manage to save his friend?', '', '', '', '', '2007-02-01 00:00:00', '22 x 16', '40', 2, '072007adventureoflittlemouse_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(527, 0, 'Photo Exhibition in the Tatami Room', 132, 1, 0, 0, '', 256, 0, 0, 0, 2, 12, '', '', 'One day, Tamotsu happens to meet an old woman with senile dementia, who believes he is her own son. He and his friend Yuichi end up visiting her place every day to look after her, and their strange relationship buildsÉ It is a story about the precious summer experience of a teenage boy.', '', '', '', '', '2007-07-01 00:00:00', '20 x 14', '198', 2, '112007peinthetatamiroom_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(528, 0, 'The Complete Illustrated Guide to Acorns in Japan', 133, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 4, 7, '|0|', '', 'From seed to germination, this first ever illustrated guide to acorns features miniature pictures of the forty different types of acorns that can be seen in Japan. Includes life size pictures of seeds and leaves.', '', '', '', '', '2004-03-01 00:00:00', '29 x 25', '156', 1, 'completeillguidetoacorn_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '2009-11-02 07:24:23', 62, 1),
(529, 35, 'The Lives of Insects', 135, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 4, 9, '', '', 'A book and CD Rom about insects, from the ''Animal Picture Book Series''. Includes about 500 different species of insect featured in about 800 photographs and an hour-long film. ', '', '', '', '', '2003-03-01 00:00:00', '30 x 24', '128', 9, 'cdr_livesofinsects_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(605, 39, 'Vol.6 - Leaf Butterflies Hiding in the Subtropical Forest', 150, 12, 135, 11, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 4, 10, '', '', 'Leaf Butterflies, which mimic dried leaves, live on the southernmost island of Japan. Why do they disguise themselves as leaves? And can we stop destroying their habitat...?', '', '', '', '', '2005-03-01 00:00:00', '25 x 21', '40', 5, 'insectsnenvironment6_b.jpg', '2008-12-24 14:43:13', 62, '2008-12-24 14:49:07', 62, 1),
(532, 31, 'Let''s Find! Different Insects', 135, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 4, 8, '', '', 'In this book, the insect loving author shows you how to spot the differences between assorted types of creepy-crawlies and become an insect whiz like him. Packed with fun challenges, colourful pictures and fascinating facts, the book is designed to help you find the odd one out from a whole range of insects.', '', '', '', '', '2007-06-01 00:00:00', '28 x 23', '32', 5, '112007ku_lfdifferentinsects_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(533, 31, 'Let''s Find! Camouflaged Insects', 135, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 4, 8, '', '', 'In order to protect themselves from predators, many insects use camouflage to make themselves difficult to spot. It''s really amazing how well some of them do it. Learn how to search out the bugs hiding in twigs, tree-bark, leaves, earth and grass in this exciting volume of the ''Expert Bug-finding With Kazuo Unno'' series. ', '', '', '', '', '2007-06-01 00:00:00', '28 x 23', '32', 5, '112007ku_lfcamouflagedinsects_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(534, 31, 'Let''s Find! Disguised Insects', 135, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 4, 8, '', '', 'You might not be able to tell at first, but some insects can cleverly disguise themselves to look like other kinds. In this lively book full of original photographs, Unno explains why some insects disguise themselves, and how to spot the fakes from the real things. With ladybirds, butterflies, ants, wasps and more! ', '', '', '', '', '2007-06-01 00:00:00', '28 x 23', '32', 5, '112007ku_lfdisguisedinsects_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(535, 32, 'Vol.1- Dandelion Fluff', 136, 12, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 4, 8, '', '', 'Dandelion seeds ride on the wind, travelling through many different places. In order to leave descendents, they use their wisdom to give birth to new lives. In this book, the structure and mechanisms of the dandelion seeds are introduced alongside colour photographs. ', '', '', '', '', '2008-03-01 00:00:00', '28 x 22', '32', 5, '052008twofsan_vol1_dandelion_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(536, 32, 'Vol.2- Violets and Ants', 136, 12, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 4, 8, '', '', 'Have you ever thought, how come there are there violets growing in a place like this? Violets use their wisdom in order to multiply. This book introduces the strange relationship between violets and the ants who transport and spread their seeds. ', '', '', '', '', '2008-03-01 00:00:00', '28 x 22', '32', 5, '052008twofsan_vol2_violets_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(537, 32, 'Vol.3- Maple Wings', 136, 12, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 4, 8, '', '', 'How do maple trees multiply, seeing as they cannot move like animals can? Well, the seeds from maple trees are shaped like wings, so that they can spin around as they fall. Their structure and mechanisms are introduced in this book. ', '', '', '', '', '2008-03-01 00:00:00', '28 x 22', '32', 5, '052008twofsan_vol3_maple_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(538, 32, 'Vol.4- Acorns and Squirrels', 136, 12, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 4, 8, '', '', 'Did you know that acorns are actually seeds? Before they grow roots and become new trees, acorns are deeply involved with squirrels and other animals who spread them around, helping the lives of those animals in turn. Find out all about the connection between acorns and squirrels. ', '', '', '', '', '2008-03-01 00:00:00', '28 x 22', '32', 5, '052008twofsan_vol4_acorns_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(539, 32, 'Vol.5- Cocklebur Thorns', 136, 12, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 4, 8, '', '', 'Cocklebur is a spiny plant known also as ''velcro weed''. In order to reproduce, they attach themselves to animals, natural substanc es and even humans. By travelling down rivers, and sticking to humans and animals, the seeds are carried far away. Take a look at how they do it. ', '', '', '', '', '2008-03-01 00:00:00', '28 x 22', '32', 5, '052008twofsan_vol5_cocklebur_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1),
(540, 0, 'Favourite Things', 137, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 3, 4, '', '', 'The children of a Nepalese rural village tell us about the things closest to their hearts. Accompanied by Kumon''s eye-catching photographs of the children in their beautiful Nepalese landscape, the book gives an easily accessible portrait of childhood in another part of the world.', '', '', '', '', '2007-10-01 00:00:00', '25 x 20', '40', 5, '112007favouritethings_b.jpg', '2008-10-10 00:00:00', 62, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1);
